                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8824" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0401</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1289 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">策马扬鞭：马钢重型H型钢厂研发团队创造力提升之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Riding a horse and whipping: The way to enhance the creativity of R &amp; D team at Masteel Heavy H-shaped steel Plant</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">韩小芳，马梅钰，林小楠，杨可玥，张士涵</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马钢重型H型钢厂</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁企业；团队创造力；团队冲突；团队学习</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Iron and steel enterprises; Team creativity; Team conflict; Team learning</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国钢铁行业正处于转型升级的关键时期，面临着市场的挑战和环境压力，同时也拥有技术创新和绿色发展的机遇。马钢重型H型钢厂抓住国家对钢铁业的改革机遇，通过“团队+项目”模式，逐渐发展为国际领先、国内最具价值的重型H型钢生产基地。本案例以马钢重型H型钢厂研发团队的组建为背景，以研发团队在三个“揭榜挂帅”项目攻关过程中遇到的困难为线索，重点描述了该团队采取一系列措施转换工作氛围、提高工作积极性、开拓创新思维，实现团队创造力提升的艰辛过程。本案例有助于学生了解团队创造力的影响因素、提升策略，掌握领导风格对团队创造力的影响，为提升团队创造力提供参考和借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">China’s steel industry is in a critical period of transformation and upgrading, facing market challenges and environmental pressure, but also has technological innovation and green development opportunities. Masteel Heavy H-shaped steel plant seized the opportunity of the national reform of the steel industry, through the “team + project” model, gradually developed into the world’s leading and the most valuable domestic heavy H-shaped steel production base. This case takes the establishment of the R&amp;D team of Masteel Heavy H-shaped Steel plant as the background, takes the difficulties encountered by the R&amp;D team in the process of tackling the key issues of three “revealing the list” as the clues, and focuses on the arduous process of the team taking a series of measures to change the working atmosphere, improve the work enthusiasm, develop innovative thinking, and achieve the improvement of team creativity. This case is helpful for students to understand the influencing factors and improvement strategies of team creativity, master the influence of leadership style on team creativity, and provide reference for improving team creativity.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">团队创造力；团队冲突；团队学习</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
